// Semantic direction:
// plugin_system allows third-party code to extend nc studio and the game engine.
// plugin_manifest declares the plugin's id, versjon, avhengighet, and utvidelsespunkt list.
// plugin_last loads the plugin binary and calls plugin_aktiver with the plugin_api handle.
// plugin_losslass calls plugin_deaktiver then unloads the binary — hot-swap capable.
// utvidelsespunkt is a named hook where plugins inject behavior (panels, systems, handlers).
// punkt_asset_behandler lets a plugin register a custom behandler for a new asset type.
// punkt_spill_system lets a plugin add an ECS system that runs in the main game loop.
// plugin_sandbox restricts what each plugin may do via sandbox_tillatelse grants.
// sandbox_brudd terminates the plugin and logs the violation rather than crashing the studio.
// nc_studio is the integrated IDE: code editor, scene editor, asset browser, and debugger.
// studio_vindus_layout arranges panels using a dok/flyt/del/fane docking system.
// kode_editor provides syntax highlighting, autocomplete, and diagnostics backed by the LSP.
// editor_autofullføring queries the language server for completions at the cursor position.
// editor_diagnostikk shows inline errors and warnings as the user types.
// editor_gå_til_definisjon jumps to the symbol's declaration in any project file.
// layout_lagre persists the panel arrangement to a user config file.
// innstillinger_synkroniser pushes user settings to a cloud profile for cross-machine sharing.

// Primitive flow:
// plugin_last(sti): last manifest -> sjekk avhengighet -> kompiler/last binær
//   -> plugin_aktiver(plugin_api) -> registrer utvidelsespunkter
//   -> oppdater plugin_liste -> tegn panel om punkt_editor_panel er registrert
// plugin_losslass(id): plugin_deaktiver -> fjern utvidelsespunkter -> losslass binær
// studio oppstart: last layout_lagre -> gjenopprett panel_dok
//   -> last plugin_liste -> plugin_last for hver aktiv plugin
//   -> vis panel_scene_hierarki / panel_inspektør / panel_ressurser / panel_konsoll
// kode_editor åpne fil: editor_fil_tre.velg -> last innhold -> syntaks_utheving
//   -> koble til LSP -> editor_diagnostikk strøm
// autofullføring: cursor posisjon -> LSP completion request -> vis forslag liste
// layout endring: panel_dok.del(panel, retning) -> layout_lagre(ny konfig)

// This defines the plugin system and nc studio IDE: extension points, sandboxed plugins,
// dockable panel layout, integrated code editor with LSP, and settings sync.

