// Semantic direction:
// sky_deploy orchestrates the full pipeline from build to live traffic.
// deploy_miljø isolates configuration between utvikling, staging, and produksjon.
// deploy_reverser rolls back to the previous deploy_historikk entry on failure.
// container_bygg produces an OCI-compatible container_bilde from the project source.
// dockerfile_generer creates a minimal Dockerfile tuned for Norscode binaries.
// bilde_registri is the OCI registry where images are pushed before deployment.
// oppdaterings_strategi_rullende replaces pods incrementally with zero downtime.
// strategi_blå_grønn runs old and new versions in parallel and cuts over instantly.
// strategi_kanarie routes a small percentage of traffic to the new version first.
// auto_skaler watches skaler_metrikk and adjusts pod_replikaer up or down.
// skaler_terskel defines the metric value at which skaler_ut or skaler_inn triggers.
// spill_server_hosting manages a pool of dedicated game server instances per region.
// server_allokering claims a server from server_pool for a new match session.
// server_frigjør returns the server to the pool when the match ends.
// infrastruktur_som_kode declares cloud resources as Norscode data; iac_anvend converges state.
// tilstand_lås prevents concurrent iac_anvend runs from corrupting tilstand_fil.
// hemmelighet_rotér generates a new secret version and updates all dependents.
// env_injeksjon injects hemmeligheter into running containers as environment variables.

// Primitive flow:
// deploy_kjør(konfig, miljø_produksjon):
//   container_bygg -> bilde_push(registri) -> oppdater pod spec
//   strategi_rullende: erstatt én pod om gangen -> pod_helse_sjekk -> fortsett
//   helse feiler -> deploy_reverser -> gjenopprett forrige bilde
// auto_skaler: overvåk cpu_grense hvert helse_intervall
//   > terskel: skaler_ut(+1 pod) | < terskel: skaler_inn(-1 pod)
// spill server: klient ber om match -> server_allokering(region)
//   -> server_pool.finn ledig -> tildel -> returner adresse til klient
//   kamp slutt -> server_frigjør -> tilbake i pool
// iac: iac_plan -> diff ønsket vs faktisk tilstand -> vis endringer
//   -> iac_anvend -> provisjoner/oppdater/slett ressurser -> oppdater tilstand_fil

// This defines cloud deployment: container builds, rolling/blue-green/canary strategies,
// autoscaling, dedicated game server pools, infrastructure as code, and secrets management.

