// Semantic direction:
// tilgjengelighet is the runtime module implementing WCAG 2.2 AA/AAA and game accessibility guidelines.
// skjermleser_melding announces text to the screen reader without moving focus.
// live_region marks an area whose changes are announced automatically by the screen reader.
// live_region_høflig waits for the user to finish before announcing; live_region_påtrengende interrupts.
// semantisk_tre mirrors the UI component tree with a11y_rolle and a11y_navn for each node.
// a11y_rolle communicates the widget's purpose to assistive technologies.
// a11y_tilstand reflects current interactive state (focused, selected, expanded, disabled).
// fokusliste is the ordered set of focusable elements; fokus_rekkefølge defines the tab sequence.
// fokus_felle keeps focus inside a modal dialog until it is dismissed.
// fokus_gjenopprett returns focus to the triggering element after a dialog closes.
// hopp_over_navigasjon provides keyboard shortcuts to skip repetitive navigation regions.
// kontrast_forhold is the luminance ratio between foreground and background colors.
// kontrast_aa_terskel is 4.5:1 for normal text; kontrast_aaa_terskel is 7:1.
// fargeblindhet_simuler applies a color matrix to preview the UI as seen by affected users.
// foretrekk_redusert_bevegelse reads the OS accessibility preference and disables animations.
// blink_terskel enforces the WCAG guideline: no more than 3 flashes per second.
// teksting provides synchronized subtitles for in-game dialogue and cutscenes.
// visuelle_varsler supplement audio cues with on-screen indicators for deaf players.
// spill_hjelpemodus offers reduced difficulty, hints, and extended timers.
// spill_automatisk_sikt assists players with motor difficulties by snapping aim to targets.
// inndata_remapping allows full rebinding of every control to any input source.

// Primitive flow:
// UI-komponent rendres: bygg semantisk_tre node -> sett a11y_rolle/navn/beskrivelse/tilstand
//   -> eksponér til OS accessibility API (NSAccessibility / AT-SPI / UIA)
// tastatur tab: fokus_neste -> finn neste i fokus_rekkefølge -> fokus_sett(element)
//   -> oppdater a11y_tilstand(fokusert) -> skjermleser_uthev
// kontrast_sjekk: beregn kontrast_forhold(forgrunn, bakgrunn)
//   < aa_terskel: logg a11y_revisjons_rapport advarsel
// foretrekk_redusert_bevegelse: les OS-preferanse -> animasjon_deaktiver -> parallaks_deaktiver
// fargeblind modus: anvend fargematrise per simuler_type -> render til skjerm
// teksting: synkroniser tekst_streng med lyd_tidsstempel -> render tekst_plassering på skjerm

// This defines accessibility: screen reader integration, semantic tree, keyboard navigation,
// color contrast, motion reduction, captioning, and game-specific accessibility features.

