// Semantic direction:
// shader_system compiles shader_kilde to multiple mål backends from one source language.
// shader_refleksjon introspects uniform names, types, and binding slots from bytecode.
// uniform_buffer groups related uniforms into a GPU-aligned block for efficient updates.
// push_konstant provides a small per-draw upload path for frequently changing values.
// materiale_instans shares the base shader but overrides specific parametere per object.
// etterbehandling_stack chains fullskjerm passes over the rendered framebuffer.
// bloom extracts bright pixels (bloom_terskel), blurs them, and additively composites.
// skarp_dybdeskarphet blurs pixels outside the focus plane using a bokehmønster convolution.
// bevegelsesuskarphet_skjerm_rom accumulates motion vectors per pixel for temporal blur.
// ssao samples a hemisphere of depth values to approximate ambient self-shadowing.
// lut_tekstur is a 3D color lookup table applied in post to achieve farge_gradering.
// tone_mapping_aces maps HDR scene luminance to LDR display range using the Academy curve.
// partikkel_gpu simulates and renders millions of partikler entirely on the GPU via compute.
// partikkel_størrelse_kurve and partikkel_farge_kurve are keyframed over partikkel_levetid.
// stråle_marsjering steps a ray through a volumetrisk scalar field to render clouds/smoke.
// sdf_kombinasjon blends signed-distance field primitives (union/intersect/subtract) for raymarching.

// Primitive flow:
// shader_kompiler: les shader_kilde (Norscode shader-språk) -> parse -> IR
//   -> krysskomipiler til mål (glsl/wgsl/msl/hlsl) -> last til GPU
// materiale bind: sett uniform_blokk(kamera, lys, modell) + uniform_sampler(teksturer)
//   -> kjør vertex_shader -> rasteriser -> fragment_shader -> framebuffer
// etterbehandling: etter scene-pass:
//   bloom: ekstraher lyse piksler -> gausisk uskarphet (N pass) -> additivt blend
//   dof: beregn circle-of-confusion per piksel -> bokeh-blur utenfor fokus
//   tone_mapping -> farge_gradering(lut) -> gamma-korreksjon -> vis
// partikkel_gpu: compute_shader per partikkel: oppdater posisjon/farge/størrelse
//   -> generer instans-buffer -> én trekk-anrop for alle partikler
// stråle_marsjering: per piksel: ray origin + dir -> marsjer N skritt
//   -> akkumuler volum_sky tetthet -> anvend lys -> alpha composite over scene

// This defines the advanced shader system: cross-backend compilation, material instances,
// post-process stack (bloom, DoF, motion blur, SSAO, LUT grading), GPU particles, and raymarching.

