// Semantic direction:
// lyd_dsp is the real-time audio processing runtime running on a dedicated audio thread.
// lyd_graf is a directed acyclic graph of graf_noder; audio flows from generators to outputs.
// dsp_bufstørrelse determines latency: smaller buffers reduce delay but increase CPU load.
// oscillator_node generates periodic waveforms at osc_frekvens with osc_amplitude.
// lfo is a low-frequency oscillator that modulates another parameter (e.g. filter cutoff).
// adsr_envelope shapes the amplitude over time: attack rises, decay falls to sustain, release fades.
// envelope_trigger starts the attack; envelope_frigjør begins the release phase.
// biquad_koeffisienter are the six filter coefficients computed from frekvens, Q, and type.
// kompressor_node reduces dynamic range above terskel_kompressor by the gitte forhold.
// reverb_impuls_respons is an impulse response IR recording convolved with the dry signal.
// delay_node echoes the signal after delay_tid milliseconds; tilbakemelding controls repeats.
// granulær_synteser chops a buffer into small korn and reassembles them for time-stretching.
// korn_stilling is the playback position in the source buffer; korn_tilfeldig adds scatter.
// steg_sekvenser is a step sequencer: each steg fires a note on the beat if steg_aktiv.
// akkord_progresjon defines a harmonic sequence; transponér shifts all notes by semitones.
// skala_kvantisér snaps freely generated pitches to the nearest note in a given scale.
// beat_hendelse fires at each takt_teller beat, synchronizing visual and gameplay events.

// Primitive flow:
// lyd_graf prosesser (per buffer):
//   oscillator -> buffer med N samples ved osc_frekvens
//   envelope_verdi * sample -> forsterker_node
//   -> filter_node: biquad_koeffisienter(frekvens, Q) -> filtrer samples
//   -> effektkjede: kompressor -> reverb (konvolusjon) -> limiter
//   -> lyd_kontekst utdata -> hardware
// adsr: trigger -> rampe opp (angrep_ms) -> rampe ned til sustain (henfall_ms)
//   frigjør -> rampe ned til 0 (utslipp_ms)
// steg_sekvenser: beat_hendelse -> les steg[takt_teller % steg_antall]
//   aktiv: spill note(frekvens, hastighet) via envelope_trigger
// granulær: hvert korn_overlapp ms: les korn_størrelse samples fra korn_stilling
//   vinduer (Hann) -> mix inn i utdatabuffer -> korn_stilling += skritt

// This defines the audio DSP and music system: node graph processing, oscillators,
// envelopes, filters, effects chain, granular synthesis, and a step sequencer.

