// Semantic direction:
// tidsserie_db is optimized for append-heavy workloads with time as the primary axis.
// målings_navn identifies the metric being recorded (e.g. "cpu_bruk", "temperatur").
// etikett provides high-cardinality dimensions for filtering (e.g. host, region, sensor_id).
// linjeprokoll is InfluxDB's line protocol: "måling,etikett=v felt=1.0 timestamp".
// lsm_tre writes data to wal_ts for durability, then merges and compresses into sorted blocks.
// gorilla_komprimering encodes floating-point timeseries using XOR delta-of-deltas (Facebook).
// delta_delta compresses integer timestamps by encoding differences of differences.
// blokkomprimering groups a time window into one block; old blocks become immutable.
// nedsampling aggregates fine-grained data into coarser granularities to save storage.
// shard_etter_tid partitions data into time shards so old shards can be dropped quickly.
// fyll_huller handles missing timestamps: forrige_verdi carries forward, lineær_interpolasjon estimates.
// kontinuerlig_spørring re-runs a spørring on a cq_intervall and writes results to cq_destinasjon.
// anomali_varsling fires when a value deviates beyond a learned baseline.
// flux_spørring is InfluxDB's functional query language for chained transformations.
// promql is Prometheus's query language for instant and range vector expressions.
// agg_persentil_ts computes p95/p99 for latency monitoring using t-digest or HDR histogram.

// Primitive flow:
// skriv: linjeprokoll_parse("cpu,host=srv1 bruk=0.72 1700000000000")
//   -> datapunkt{måling, etiketter, felt, ts} -> wal_ts.append -> ack til klient
//   bakgrunn: wal_ts -> lsm_komprimering -> blokk med gorilla_komprimering
// spørring: fra("cpu") |> rekkevidde(siste: 1t) |> filter_flux(etikett["host"] == "srv1")
//   |> vindu_fast(hvert: 5m) |> agg_gjennom_snitt_ts()
//   -> finn shards for tidsrekkevidde -> dekomprimér blokker -> anvend filtre -> aggreger
// nedsampling: kontinuerlig_spørring hvert 1t:
//   aggreger 1min-data til 1t-gjennomsnittsverdi -> skriv til "cpu_1t" måling
//   oppbevarings_policy: slett rå 1min-data etter 7 dager
// varsling: terskel_varsling(agg_gjennomsnitt > 0.9 i 5min) -> tilstand_varsling
//   send til varslings_kanal (Slack, PagerDuty) -> tilstand_ok når under terskel

// This defines the time series database: line protocol ingestion, LSM-tree storage with
// Gorilla compression, downsampling, continuous queries, window functions, gap filling,
// threshold alerting, Flux queries, and PromQL compatibility.

