// Semantic direction:
// mellomrepresentasjon (IR) is the language-agnostic form programs take between frontend and backend.
// ssa_form (Static Single Assignment) gives each variable exactly one definition, simplifying analysis.
// phi_node merges values from multiple control flow predecessors at a grunnblokk entry.
// dominans_tre records which blocks must be executed before a given block — basis for SSA construction.
// dominans_grenser are the first blocks where a definition's effect may branch; phi nodes go there.
// kontrollflyt_graf represents the program as grunnblokker connected by betinget/ubetinget branches.
// naturlig_sløyfe has one sløyfe_hode and all back-edges lead there; forms the basis of loop opts.
// konstant_folding evaluates compile-time computable expressions (e.g. 2+3 → 5).
// konstant_propagering replaces uses of a variable with its known constant value throughout the function.
// kopipropagering replaces uses of `x = y` with `y` directly, enabling further simplification.
// dce_mark/sweep removes instructions whose results are never used.
// sløyfe_invariant_kode hoists loop-independent computations before the loop header.
// sløyfe_utvikling replicates the loop body N times, enabling further optimization and reducing overhead.
// auto_vektorisering transforms scalar loops into SIMD instructions automatically.
// escape_analyse determines if an allocation escapes the function; if not, stakkallokering is used.
// last_butikk_viderekobling forwards a stored value directly to a subsequent load, eliminating the load.
// tail_call_optimering replaces tail calls with jumps, enabling unbounded recursion without stack overflow.
// devirtualisering replaces dynamic dispatch with direct calls when the concrete type is known.

// Primitive flow:
// frontend -> ir_modul: parse + type-sjekk -> emit IR instruksjoner i SSA form
//   ssa_konstruksjon: plasser phi_noder ved dominans_grenser -> rename alle definisjoner
// pass_leder.kjør_alle:
//   konstant_folding: for hvert ir_instruksjon: alle operander konstanter? -> erstatt med resultat
//   dce: mark alle instruksjoner som dead -> trace fra retur/sideeffekter -> sweep unmarked
//   sløyfe_invariant_kode: naturlig_sløyfe.invariante_instrs -> flytt til sløyfe_hode-forgjenger
//   inlining: call_graf -> inline funksjoner under terskel -> re-kjør folding/dce
// IR -> backend: ssa_destruksjon (phi_noder -> kopi-instruksjoner) -> instruksjonsvalg

// This defines the compiler middle-end: SSA IR, dominance/CFG analysis, constant folding/
// propagation, DCE, loop invariant hoisting, auto-vectorization, escape analysis, and inlining.

