// Semantic direction:
// digital_tvilling is a live virtual representation of a physical asset, synchronized via sensor data.
// tvilling_modell holds the physics-based or data-driven equations describing the asset's behavior.
// tvilling_historikk stores all past tilstand snapshots for trend analysis and replay.
// iot_enhet represents a physical sensor/actuator; enhet_provisjonering enrolls it securely.
// mqtt_qos levels: 0 = fire-and-forget, 1 = at-least-once, 2 = exactly-once.
// mqtt_will is a message the broker sends on behalf of a client that disconnects unexpectedly.
// lorawan is a low-power wide-area protocol for battery-operated sensors in remote locations.
// ønsket_tilstand is the cloud-requested configuration; rapportert_tilstand is what the device confirms.
// tilstands_delta is the diff between ønsket and rapportert that the device must apply.
// fysisk_modell encodes ODEs or FEM equations; simulering_fremskritt integrates them forward in time.
// prediktivt_vedlikehold predicts component failure from sensor trends.
// rul_estimering (Remaining Useful Life) estimates how long a component will function.
// kantskyberegning runs lokal_inferens on the kant_node to reduce latency and bandwidth.
// kant_filter_iot discards irrelevant readings before forwarding to the cloud.
// tvilling_graf links tvilling_noder by relasjon_type — e.g. fabrikk inneholder linjer inneholder maskiner.

// Primitive flow:
// sensor data: mqtt_klient.publiser("fabrikk/maskin1/temp", 87.3)
//   IoT hub motter -> koble til tvilling_id -> tvilling_oppdater(sensor_verdi)
//   anomali_iot: verdi > terskel -> varsling + prediktivt_vedlikehold kjøres
// ønsket/rapportert: sky sender ønsket_tilstand{setpunkt: 70}
//   enhet mottar -> anvend -> rapportert_tilstand{setpunkt: 70} -> tilstands_delta = {}
// simulering: fysisk_modell(maskin) -> differensialligninger for varmeoverføring
//   simulering_fremskritt(dt=1sek) -> oppdatert tvilling_tilstand
//   sammenlignet mot sensor_verdi -> avvik > terskel -> simulering_kalibrering
// kantskyberegning: sensor_verdi ankommer kant_node
//   lokal_inferens(ml_modell) -> normal | anomali
//   normal: kant_aggregering(hvert 60sek) -> batch til sky
//   anomali: øyeblikkelig sky_synkronisering_iot

