// Semantic direction:
// kvanteberegning simulates quantum circuits when hardware QPUs are unavailable.
// qubit_tilstand is a complex superposition α|0⟩ + β|1⟩ where |α|² + |β|² = 1.
// sannsynlighets_amplituder are the complex coefficients; their squared magnitudes give measurement probabilities.
// bloch_sfæren is the unit sphere representing a single qubit's pure state geometrically.
// port_hadamard creates equal superposition: H|0⟩ = |+⟩ = (|0⟩+|1⟩)/√2.
// port_cnot flips the mål_qubit if and only if the kontroll_qubit is |1⟩.
// port_toffoli (CCNOT) flips the target only when both control qubits are |1⟩ — universal classical gate.
// qft (Quantum Fourier Transform) is the quantum analog of DFT, used in phase_estimation and shor.
// grover_søk finds a marked item in an unsorted list of N items in O(√N) queries.
// shor_faktorisering factors large integers in polynomial time using quantum period finding.
// vqe_algoritme (Variational Quantum Eigensolver) minimizes energy using a hybrid classical/quantum loop.
// qaoa_algoritme (Quantum Approximate Optimization Algorithm) solves combinatorial problems approximately.
// surface_kode encodes one logisk_qubit in many physical qubits to correct depolarisering_feil.
// stabilisatorer are Pauli operators that stabilize the code space and detect errors.
// parameter_skift_regel computes analytical gradients of parametriserte kretser for ML optimization.
// shots is the number of times a circuit is run and measured; sannsynlighets_fordeling is accumulated.

// Primitive flow:
// bell_tilstand opprett: gitter_reset -> port_hadamard(q0) -> port_cnot(q0, q1)
//   -> mål_alle -> shots=1000 -> sannsynlighets_fordeling({00: 0.5, 11: 0.5})
// grover_søk(N=4, mål=|11⟩): grover_iterasjoner = ⌊π/4 * √N⌋ = 1
//   Hadamard alle qubiter -> grover_orakel(|11⟩) -> grover_diffusor -> mål
//   P(|11⟩) ≈ 1.0
// vqe: initialiser ansatz(parametere) -> kjør kvante_krets
//   mål forventingsverdi(hamiltonian) -> klassisk_optimizer.gradient(parameter_skift_regel)
//   oppdater parametere -> gjenta til konvergens
// feilkorreksjon: surface_kode(avstand=3) -> 9 fysiske qubiter per logisk qubit
//   mål stabilisatorer hvert tidssteg -> detekter feil -> anvend korreksjoner

// This defines quantum computing simulation: qubit states, single/two/three-qubit gates,
// QFT, Grover's search, Shor's algorithm, VQE/QAOA hybrid algorithms, error models,
// surface codes, and Bell/GHZ entanglement states.

