// Semantic direction:
// generativ_testing automatically finds counterexamples by generating random inputs.
// egenskap_for_alle states a property that must hold for all generated inputs.
// gen_rekursiv generates nested structures (trees, JSON) by recursively composing generators.
// gen_frekvens weights multiple generators by relative probability.
// størrelse_gjennom controls how inputs grow from small to large over gt_kjøringer.
// egenskap_anta adds a precondition; inputs that don't satisfy it are skipped without counting as failures.
// egenskap_klassifiser labels generated inputs (e.g. "tom", "liten", "stor") for distribution reporting.
// krymp_sekvens finds the minimalt_moteksempel by systematically reducing failing inputs.
// krymp_heltall tries 0, then narrows toward the failing value by halving the range.
// krymp_liste removes elements one at a time and tries smaller sublists.
// eksempel_database persists previously found failures so they are always re-tested first.
// stateful_testing generates kommando_sekvenser and verifies that the system matches the system_modell.
// kommando_precondition skips commands invalid in the current modell_tilstand.
// kommando_postcondition asserts that the real system and the modell agree after each command.
// coverage_feedback_gen uses program coverage to guide mutation toward unexplored branches.
// strukturert_fuzzing generates syntactically valid inputs using the grammar to reach deep paths.
// round_trip checks that serialize(deserialize(x)) == x for codec implementations.
// differensiell_testing compares two implementations and asserts they produce identical outputs.
// oracle_test compares against a referanse_implementasjon known to be correct.

// Primitive flow:
// egenskap "reversering er involutiv":
//   for_alle_gen(gen_liste(gen_heltall)) { liste ->
//     egenskap_påstand(liste.reverser().reverser() == liste) }
//   > gt_kjøringer(1000) -> alle passerer
// moteksempel funnet: egenskap_påstand(a + b == b + a) for flyt
//   input: a=NaN, b=1 -> NaN + 1 ≠ 1 + NaN (begge NaN men ikke ==)
//   krymp_sekvens: prøv (0, NaN) -> (NaN, 0) -> minimalt: (NaN, 0)
// stateful: modell(kø) { enqueue(x): tilstand.push(x) | dequeue: tilstand.pop() }
//   generer 100-kommando sekvens -> kjør mot ekte kø + modell
//   tilstands_samsvar(ekte, modell) -> hevd likt innhold etter hvert steg
// round_trip: for_alle_gen(gen_json_verdi) { v ->
//   egenskap_påstand(json_parse(json_stringify(v)) == v) }

// This defines generative and property-based testing: typed generators with recursive
// composition, shrinking to minimal counterexamples, stateful model-based testing,
// coverage-guided fuzzing, and formal properties (commutativity, idempotency, round-trip).

