// Semantic direction:
// bevis_assistert uses the Curry-Howard correspondence: proposisjoner are types, bevis are programs.
// pi_type is the dependent function type Π(x:A).B(x) — the type of bevis of universal statements.
// sigma_type is the dependent pair Σ(x:A).B(x) — a witness x together with a bevis of B(x).
// subset_type is {x : A | P(x)} — values of type A satisfying predicate P, bundled with the bevis.
// refinement_bevis is the proof term witnessing that a value satisfies its refinement_predikat.
// refleksivitet proves a = a for any a; symmetri proves a = b → b = a.
// kongruens proves f(a) = f(b) given a = b by applying the function to both sides.
// j_eliminator is the induction principle for proporsjonell_likhet (the J-rule).
// eksistens constructs a sigma_type: provide a witness and a bevis.
// taktikk_simp applies a set of rewrite lemmas automatically to reduce goals.
// taktikk_omega decides linear arithmetic over integers automatically.
// taktikk_aesop is a general-purpose proof search tactic combining simplification and backtracking.
// terminering_mål is a well-founded measure that strictly decreases in each recursive call.
// verifisert_sortering is a proven-correct sorting algorithm with a bevis that output is sorted and a permutation.
// ekstraksjon generates runnable Norscode code from a verified bevis term.

// Primitive flow:
// bevis associativitet av tillegg: teorem add_assoc(a b c : Nat) : a + (b + c) = (a + b) + c
//   taktikk_induction a
//   base: 0 + (b + c) = (0 + b) + c -> taktikk_rfl
//   steg: antar ind_hyp: n + (b + c) = (n + b) + c
//     vis: (n+1) + (b+c) = ((n+1)+b)+c -> unfold + -> kongruens(ind_hyp) -> taktikk_rfl
// subset_type: {n : Heltall | n > 0} -> sigma_type(Heltall, gt_zero_bevis)
//   konstruer: sigma(5, bevis_at_5_gt_0) : {n | n > 0}
// verifisert_sortering: spec at: output er sortert OG er_permutasjon(input, output)
//   bevis ved strukturell_induksjon på listen -> ekstraksjon -> ren Norscode funksjon
// terminering: fn fib(n) terminerer fordi terminering_mål = n
//   velfundert_relasjon = < på Nat -> kompilator aksepterer rekursjonen

// This defines proof-assisted programming: dependent pi/sigma types, subset types, the J-rule,
// logical connectives as types, a tactic language (rfl/induction/simp/omega/aesop), termination
// proofs, and extraction of verified programs to runnable Norscode.

