// Semantic direction:
// lsp_server implements the Language Server Protocol for Norscode IDE integration.
// json_rpc is the transport protocol: request/response pairs over stdio or TCP.
// init_kapabiliteter negotiates which LSP features the server and client support.
// sync_inkrementell_lsp sends only dok_endring deltas rather than full file content.
// diagnostikk reports parse errors, type errors, and lint warnings with diag_rekkevidde.
// diag_pull_modell allows the client to request diagnostics on demand (LSP 3.17+).
// fullfør_element represents one completion candidate with its etikett, type, and dokumentasjon.
// fullfør_løs lazily loads detailed element_dokumentasjon when the user selects a candidate.
// hover_innhold is the markdown or plaintext shown in the hover popup.
// definisjon jumps to the declaration site of the symbol under the cursor.
// referanser returns all usage sites of a symbol across the workspace.
// kode_handlinger suggest fixes (quick_fix) or improvements (refaktorér) at a position.
// inlay_hints overlay inferred types and parameter names inline in the editor view.
// semantiske_tokens colors identifiers by their semantic role (function, type, variable).
// relative_encoding encodes token positions as deltas for compact transmission.
// call_hierarchy shows which functions call or are called by the current function.
// rename_symbol renames a symbol across all files in the workspace atomically.

// Primitive flow:
// åpne fil: klient → textDocument/didOpen{uri, text, version}
//   server: parse + type-sjekk -> publiser_diagnostikker{diag_liste}
// autofullføring: klient → textDocument/completion{posisjon}
//   server: finn token ved cursor -> query symboler i scope
//   -> bygg fullfør_elementer med type + dokumentasjon -> svar
// gå til definisjon: klient → textDocument/definition{posisjon}
//   server: finn symbol ved cursor -> slå opp definisjon_sted -> returner lokasjon
// kode handling: klient → textDocument/codeAction{rekkevidde, diagnostikker}
//   server: finn quick_fix for hvert diag -> kode_handlinger liste
//   klient velger -> workspace/applyEdit -> redigering anvend
// rename: klient → textDocument/rename{posisjon, ny_navn}
